snippet.title: Sundered Launch Trailer - Resist Or Embrace
snippet.description:
Sundered is out NOW on PC/Mac/Linux and PS4!

Sundered is a horrifying fight for survival and sanity, a hand-drawn epic from the creators of Jotun.

Learn more: thunderlotusgames.com
